    <item>
      <title>小米寻求53亿美元的股票出售来资助EV扩展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/xiaomi-seeks-up-to-5-3-billion-in-share-share</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小米公司（小米公司）开始了一笔股票的销售，该股票的出售可能高达53亿美元，利用了中国公司股票价格的增长，以帮助筹集资金以扩大其电动汽车业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/xiaomi-seeks-up-to-5-3-billion-in-share-share</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Mar 2025 09:06:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
