      <title>贝莱德转向美国垃圾债券，欧洲央行设置为缓慢切割</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-24/blackrock-shifts-to-us-junk-bonds-with-ecb-set-to-slow-rate-cuts</link>
